name: Twilight
description:
Quality hand painted with black nail polish with a magenta glitter gradient on the tips. There is one full magenta glitter accent nail. The design is sealed with two coats of quality top coat for extra shine and protection. 

*Each set includes 12 nails that can easily be filed to fit your unique nail shape. 
 
*Nail glue included when you order at least 2 sets
 
(Can also do requests for different designs and/or colors. All sales final.)
